# Required Fields by Notification Type

General Type       | Request Type           | Required Fields
------------------ | -------------------- | ---------------------------------------
Loan / Rental      | created (new loan)     | loan_id, client_name, car_name, due_date
                   | updated (loan update)  | loan_id, car_name
                   | canceled (loan cancel) | loan_id, car_name, client_name
                   | returned (car returned)| loan_id, car_name, client_name
                   | overdue (late return)  | loan_id, car_name, client_name, due_date

Transfer           | transfer_created       | car_name, source_agency, destination_agency, depart_date
                   | transfer_arrived       | car_name, destination_agency

Maintenance        | maintenance_due        | car_name, maintenance_type, due_date
                   | maintenance_completed  | car_name, maintenance_type

Payment / Invoice  | payment_received       | amount, client_name, payment_method
                   | invoice_created        | invoice_id, client_name, amount

Generic / Fallback | generic                | message
